    "This process ensures a balanced representation of various fault labeling categories within the clustered dataset.",
    "Before the LLM is fine-tuned with the prepared locomotive maintenance corpora, these corpora must be converted from their current Excel format to the JSON format required by the UIE.",
    "Additionally, the positions of entities within the text must be annotated.",
    "Typically, this conversion and annotation process involves manual data annotation, which requires a high level of business knowledge and expertise from the annotators.",
    "However, manual annotation is not only time-consuming but also inefficient, presenting considerable challenges to the overall annotation process."
